title: Marco Rubio arrives in Budapest to meet Viktor Orbán ahead of Hungary elections – Europe live
summary_full: Rubio visits Trump ally Orbán to help shore up his position ahead of elections in April, with the two countries expected to sign a civilian nuclear deal later todayWe have some images come through from the newswires of Marco Rubio in Budapest:Hungary’s 12 April election is set to be one of the year’s most consequential in the EU. Voters will choose a new 199-seat national assembly under the country’s mixed electoral system, with Viktor Orbán facing his biggest electoral challenge after 16 years of uninterrupted power.
